# 🔄 SYSTEM WORKFLOW

1. User logs in via Firebase Auth
2. User sets helper availability toggle
3. User creates request OR presses SOS
4. Voice/text processed via AI
5. Stored in Firestore
6. Nearby helpers (toggle ON) get notified
7. Helper accepts request
8. Chat initiated
9. Status updates tracked
10. Request resolved

